{"id":581165306,"lang":"java","time":"1 month, 1 week","timestamp":1635889465,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/581165306/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Add Strings","memory":"38.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public String addStrings(String num1, String num2) {\n        \n StringBuilder sb= new StringBuilder();\n        \n    int al= num1.length()-1;\n    int bl=num2.length()-1;\n    \n    int carry=0; \n  \n    while(al>=0 || bl>=0 )\n    {\n      int sum = carry;\n      if (al >= 0) \n          sum =sum+ num1.charAt(al--) -'0' ;\n      if (bl >= 0) \n          sum=sum + num2.charAt(bl--)-'0';\n\n       sb.append(sum%10);\n        carry= sum/10;  \n        \n\n    }\n        \n    if(carry!=0) sb.append(carry);\n    \n        return sb.reverse().toString();\n    }}\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"add-strings"}
